---
title: Mumbai Pork Meatballs & Bombay Veggie Toss with Garlic Yoghurt & Flaked Almonds
description: It may not look like there’s much to this bowl but you’ll be surprised by the depth of flavour in the pork meatballs, like the mouth watering spices for both the meatballs and roasted veggies. There’s even garlic aromas in the yoghurt, perfect for drizzling over.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
